"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1931522-Iga-Swiatek-Olympics-2024-bronze-medal-tears\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Iga Swiatekhas revealed that she spent six hours crying after feeling like someone \\\"broke her heart\\\" when she lost in the semi-final of theOlympics, blowing her chance to fight for a gold medal.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 5, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.637866873202667e-15, \"text\": \"Iga\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But just a day later, the world No.\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 233, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1 returned to the same court and won the bronze medal.\", \"from\": 234, \"to\": 288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After a rollercoaster 24 hours, Swiatek confessed that her emotional run had taught her to show more \\\"humility\\\" after realising that she stopped playing for herself and started playing for others when the pressure got to her.\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 514, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Swiatek took her semi-final loss to Qinwen Zheng very hard.\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 559, \"end\": 564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.1391126364225396e-12, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She debated the match point with the umpireand did not shake the official's hand at the end.She then walked away from a TV interview to cry and skipped the rest of her media duties.\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 803, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 873, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 890, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She managed to, in her own words, \\\"get it together\\\" in time for the bronze medal playoff where she beat Anna Karolina Schmiedlova 6-2 6-1 to claim her first Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 1063, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After the victory, the 23-year-old explained just how emotional she was before forcing herself to turn it around.\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You do not wanna know,\\\" Swiatek laughed when asked how she spent the last 24 hours.\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1263, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well truth be told, I do not remember, maybe I cried like that after losing in Australia after I won my first Grand Slam.\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1344, \"end\": 1353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9209108204231303, \"rank\": 0.06108852033230423, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After Roland Garros that was in October and then we started the season in Australia, I lost and I cried for like three days basically.\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1521, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1393, \"end\": 1406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999999996521183, \"rank\": 3.477605446517471e-10, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}, {\"begin\": 1461, \"end\": 1470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9209108204231303, \"rank\": 0.06108852033230423, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think if I wasn't playing today I would cry [for] over a week.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1586, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I needed to get it together.\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I probably cried for like six hours yesterday.\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was really tough.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know, sometimes it feels like it's sport and it's tennis and usually I am able to have the distance to all of it and just understand that it's only one part of my life but this time it was like somebody really broke my heart, you know?\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1933, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's crazy, honestly.\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1958, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the five-time Grand Slam champion will use her Olympics experience as a lesson to be learned.\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 2057, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She continued: \\\"Because of the fact that I happened, I know I still have so much work to do to understand myself and what's happening to me sometimes a little bit better.\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2228, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because of the fact that I am No.\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2262, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1 for such a long time and I won so many tournaments, I literally felt that I can handle everything, you know?\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2373, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy    \\\"And this tournament showed me that's still not the case.\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2592, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So actually, I was maybe a little bit too arrogant with myself because I thought that I have handled so much pressure before that I think I am going to handle this one as well.\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And now I am motivated to work even harder and I think I am going to have a bit more humility with everything so I think this actually can end up with me working better in the future.\\\"\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not the first time that Swiatek has struggled at the Olympics - she was also in tears when she lost in the second round in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 3106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3084, \"end\": 3089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9997092230015014, \"rank\": 0.000290267421506259, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after her semi-final match against Zheng - which she branded \\\"one of the toughest losses I probably ever had in my career\\\" - she realised the extent of her struggles at the Games.\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3146, \"end\": 3151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.1391126364225396e-12, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Honestly, during the competition, I wasn't really aware that it was so much because I understood that I was stressed and I accepted that it was going to be that way.\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3458, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was in Tokyo and I saw how hard it is and how different this tournament is than what I had on tour.\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3468, \"end\": 3473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9997092230015014, \"rank\": 0.000290267421506259, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think [the issue was] playing these few matches in a row without having a little bit of time to not really think about tennis, which I am more used to now when we have longer 1000 tournaments and Grand Slams,\\\" she explained.\", \"from\": 3561, \"to\": 3787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This plus the fact that I actually realised yesterday that I wasn't really playing for myself, I was more playing for everybody else, for the country, for my team, for everybody that hoped that I am going to win a medal and probably win a gold medal.\", \"from\": 3789, \"to\": 4040, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I talked about it, I tried to work through it but I wasn't quite aware of how deep it was in me and how much of a baggage that was.\", \"from\": 4041, \"to\": 4180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I only realised that after I lost and honestly I know I have not been playing my A-game here probably, I wasn't feeling like I can move really naturally and in a way that I am used to, especially on clay.\\\"\", \"from\": 4181, \"to\": 4389, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Carlos Alcaraz thrashes Auger-Aliassime as Spaniard one win from Olympic gold  Do not miss:Andrey Rublev deletes controversial Khelif post after Russian sparked backlash  Do not miss:Novak Djokovic shows true colours with message to Andy Murray after retirement  We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 4391, \"to\": 4775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4403, \"end\": 4417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 4494, \"end\": 4507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrey_Rublev\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrey Rublev\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrey_Rublev\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrey_Rublev\"}, {\"begin\": 4548, \"end\": 4555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.999810057409109, \"rank\": 0.0001850638293474101, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4586, \"end\": 4600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 4636, \"end\": 4647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.4635260423784e-59, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 4776, \"to\": 4852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 4853, \"to\": 4885, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy    Although she bounced back for the bronze medal playoff, Swiatek confessed that she was still feeling mixed emotions when she sat on her bench after beating Schmiedlova.\", \"from\": 4886, \"to\": 5080, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"When I sat down after the match I was really confused because I still feel like I lost yesterday and it was a huge loss but on the other hand I won today and it was tough as well so I should be proud of that.\", \"from\": 5081, \"to\": 5300, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a lot of mixed emotions and still is.\", \"from\": 5302, \"to\": 5349, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I am going to have a few days of negative emotions from yesterday and then they are going to pass and I am going to remember winning the bronze medal - I hope so, I guess.\\\"\", \"from\": 5350, \"to\": 5530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As Swiatek tries to learn how to cope better with the pressure, she will be using one of her fellow young Grand Slam champions as an example.\", \"from\": 5532, \"to\": 5673, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I actually am watchingCarlos Alcarazand I can see he's enjoying every minute of it and he's a great example actually of how to handle all of that well,\\\" she smiled.\", \"from\": 5674, \"to\": 5839, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 5841, \"to\": 6010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5978, \"end\": 5991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6972471726829604e-26, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 6012, \"to\": 6079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6027, \"end\": 6040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6972471726829604e-26, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"